hton|pos=SR}}\n\n|legend1=[[File:Injury icon 2.svg|8px]] Injured\n|coach=[[Adrian Lam]]\n|assistant=[[John Winder]]\n|assistant2=[[Matty Peet]]\n|assistant3=[[Darrell Goulding]]}}\n\n==2020 transfers ==\n\n'''Gains'''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Player !! Club !! Contract !! Date\n|-\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mitch Clark (rugby league)|Mitch Clark]] || [[Leigh Centurions]] || 3 Years || June 2019 <ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.wiganwarriors.com/news/2019-06-06-in-focus-mitch-clark | title=In focus: Mitch Clark &#124; News &#124; Wigan Warriors}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jake Bibby]] || [[Salford Red Devils]] || 2 Years || June 2019 <ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.wiganwarriors.com/news/2019-06-06-jake-bibby-joins-wigan |title = Jake Bibby joins Wigan &#124; News &#124; Wigan Warriors}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Jackson Hastings]] || [[Salford Red Devils]] || 2 Years || June 2019 <ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.wiganwarriors.com/news/2019-07-08-hastings-to-become-a-warrior |title = Hastings to become a Warrior &#124; News &#124; Wigan Warriors}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[George Burgess (rugby league)|George Burgess]] || [[South Sydney Rabbitohs]] || 3 Years || July 2019 <ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.wiganwarriors.com/news/2019-07-28-wigan-lure-george-burgess-to-super-league | title=Wigan lure George Burgess to Super League &#124; News &#124; Wigan Warriors}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{Flagicon|AUS}} [[Bevan French]] || [[Parramatta Eels]] || 2 Years || July 2019 <ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.wiganwarriors.com/news/2019-07-27-bevan-french-signs-with-the-warriors |title = Bevan French signs with the Warriors &#124; News &#124; Wigan Warriors}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} Kai Pearce-Paul || [[London Broncos]] || 4 years || November 2019 <ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.wiganwarriors.com/news/2019-11-08-wigan-sign-broncos-youngster |title = Wigan sign Broncos youngster &#124; News &#124; Wigan Warriors}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n'''Losses'''\n{| class=\"w